コメント件数：#{diet_method.diet_method_comments.count}
- diet_method.diet_method_comments.each do |diet_method_comment|
  = attachment_image_tag diet_method.customer, :profile_image, fallback: "no_image.png", size: "70x70"
  = diet_method_comment.customer.name
  = diet_method_comment.created_at.strftime('%Y/%m/%d')
  = diet_method_comment.body
  - if diet_method_comment.customer = current_customer
    = link_to "削除", diet_method_diet_method_comment_path(diet_method_comment.diet_method, diet_method_comment), method: :delete, remote: true